---
import ToolLayout from '../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/lab-hud.css';
---

<ToolLayout
  title="ISS 卫星过顶 · 几点抬头看"
  description="根据你的位置，算出国际空间站未来 48 小时何时从天上飞过、有多接近头顶。"
  currentSlug="sat-pass"
>
  <h1 slot="header">卫星过顶</h1>
  <p class="intro">
    国际空间站（ISS）从你家天上飞过时，往往是肉眼可见的亮点。本页告诉你<strong>下次该几点抬头</strong>，以及飞得多正头顶。
  </p>

  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Oxanium:wght@500;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />

  <div class="lab-hud lab-hero">
    <p class="lab-story">
      <strong>这页干嘛：</strong>查<strong>ISS 过顶时刻</strong>。仰角越高越接近「正头顶」，越好找。星历用仓库内 TLE 快照（非实时联网）。
    </p>

    <canvas id="sat-canvas" class="lab-hero-canvas" aria-label="ISS 过顶天穹预测"></canvas>

    <div class="lab-cards" aria-label="下次过顶">
      <div class="lab-card">
        <span class="lab-card-k">下次过顶</span>
        <span class="lab-card-v amber" id="sat-card-when">计算中…</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lab-card">
        <span class="lab-card-k">最高有多正头顶</span>
        <span class="lab-card-v" id="sat-card-el">—</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lab-card">
        <span class="lab-card-k">最高时朝哪看</span>
        <span class="lab-card-v" id="sat-card-az">—</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="lab-hero-caption lab-amber" id="sat-next">计算中…</p>

    <details class="lab-details" open>
      <summary>过顶时刻表（点一行可重播该次轨迹）</summary>
      <p class="lab-note">星历快照 <span class="lab-amber" id="sat-updated">—</span> · <span id="sat-geo-note">—</span></p>
      <div class="lab-controls">
        <label>纬度 <input type="number" id="sat-lat" step="0.0001" /></label>
        <label>经度 <input type="number" id="sat-lon" step="0.0001" /></label>
        <button type="button" class="lab-btn" id="sat-apply">重算</button>
        <button type="button" class="lab-btn secondary" id="sat-gps">定位</button>
      </div>
      <p class="lab-meta" id="sat-status">—</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>出现</th><th>飞到最高</th><th>消失</th><th>有多正头顶</th><th>朝哪看</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="sat-rows"></tbody>
      </table>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div class="lab-related">
    <h2>相关</h2>
    <a href="/tools/astro-today">今日星空</a>
    <a href="/space">轻星图</a>
    <a href="/tools/orbit-lab">轨道实验</a>
  </div>
</ToolLayout>

<script>
  import { bootSatPass } from '../../scripts/sat-pass/main';
  bootSatPass();
</script>
